* ===========================================================================
* VERSIONE STRUTTURATA CLASSICA - M/M/2 VALIDATION (λ=1.6, μ=1.0, c=2)
* ===========================================================================

* ---- 1. TABELLA DI QUANTILI PER LA DISTRIBUZIONE ESPONENZIALE ----
EXPON    FUNCTION  RN1,C24
0,0/.1,.104/.2,.222/.3,.356/.4,.509/.5,.693/.6,.916/.7,1.2/.75,1.38
.8,1.6/.84,1.83/.88,2.12/.9,2.3/.92,2.52/.94,2.81/.95,2.99/.96,3.2
.97,3.5/.98,3.9/.99,4.6/.995,5.3/.998,6.2/.999,7/.9998,8

* ---- 2. ALLOCAZIONE RISORSE (c = 2) ----
SERVERS  STORAGE   2

         SIMULATE

* ---- 3. DINAMICA DELLE TRANSAZIONI ---------------------------------------
* IAT: lambda = 1.6 -> Media = 1/1.6 = 0.625
         GENERATE  0.625,FN$EXPON
         QUEUE     SYSTEM
         QUEUE     WAIT
         ENTER     SERVERS
         DEPART    WAIT
* ST: mu = 1.0 -> Media = 1/1.0 = 1.0
         ADVANCE   1.0,FN$EXPON
         LEAVE     SERVERS
         DEPART    SYSTEM
         TERMINATE

* ---- 4. CONTROLLO TEMPO DI RUN (Timer aggiornato a 100000) ---------------
         GENERATE  100000
         TERMINATE 1
         START     1
